      <body>This is interesting. But unless i'm mistaken this requires a special frontend server setup (Apache in your article). So the user would need to explicitely opt into this cause otherwise page caching would break if the frontend server hasn't been set up accordingly?

In this case why not wrap this up as a tiny plugin and publish it on rails-i18n.org?</body>
