special frontend server setup (Apache in your article). So the user
would need to explicitely opt into this cause otherwise page
caching would break if the frontend server hasn't been set up
accordingly?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this case why not wrap this up as a tiny plugin and publish
it on rails-i18n.org?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
